  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Frontline Survivors is an intense top-down shooter with roguelite elements that puts you in the boots of a soldier fighting for survival on the battlefield. With countless enemies coming at you from all sides, you will need to use all your skills and strategy to stay alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you progress through the game, you'll have the opportunity to level up and choose upgrades that can improve your weapon efficiency as well as give you a range of special abilities. Whether you want to focus on skills and speed, or go in guns blazing, there are plenty of options to suit your playstyle.<br><br>With immersive gameplay, challenging enemies, and a range of customizations to unlock, Frontline Survivors is a must-play for any fan of top-down shooters. <br><br>Are you ready to join the fight and emerge as a survivor on the frontlines?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Capture camps and destroy objectives to conquer the battlefield<br></li><li> Command allies to help you beat the enemy<br></li><li> Upgrade your character in various ways<br></li><li> Multiple characters to choose from with their own skills and gameplay<br></li><li> Unlock new weapons to obliterate your enemies</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Frontline Survivors is an intense top-down shooter with roguelite elements that puts you in the boots of a soldier fighting for survival on the battlefield. With countless enemies coming at you from all sides, you will need to use all your skills and strategy to stay alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you progress through the game, you'll have the opportunity to level up and choose upgrades that can improve your weapon efficiency as well as give you a range of special abilities. Whether you want to focus on skills and speed, or go in guns blazing, there are plenty of options to suit your playstyle.<br><br>With immersive gameplay, challenging enemies, and a range of customizations to unlock, Frontline Survivors is a must-play for any fan of top-down shooters. <br><br>Are you ready to join the fight and emerge as a survivor on the frontlines?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Capture camps and destroy objectives to conquer the battlefield<br></li><li> Command allies to help you beat the enemy<br></li><li> Upgrade your character in various ways<br></li><li> Multiple characters to choose from with their own skills and gameplay<br></li><li> Unlock new weapons to obliterate your enemies</li></ul>",
